- Take an event in, count it
- Validate that incoming event count is numeric
- Allow de-duplication over a range (i.e. only count at most once in a hour,
  day, week, etc.)
- Listen for counting events from:
  - STDIN
  - UDP
  - TDP
- Output counting events to:
  - STDOUT (no aggregation)
  - file
  - database
- Upon count:
  - Print to STDOUT
  - add to metrics and update aggregates
- Streaming events, counts updated as they come in
